<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Discord Panel - <%= title %></title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: #1a1a2e;
      color: #eee;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .container {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #fff; }
    p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 500px; }
    .btn-discord {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      background: #5865F2;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-discord:hover { background: #4752C4; }
    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      max-width: 700px;
    }
    .feature {
      background: #16213e;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #0f3460;
    }
    .feature h3 { color: #5865F2; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .feature p { font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Discord Panel</h1>
    <p>Connectez-vous avec Discord pour gérer votre compte, rejoindre des serveurs et bien plus.</p>
    <a href="/login" class="btn-discord">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
        <path d="M20.317 4.37a19.791 19.791 0 0 0-4.885-1.515.074.074 0 0 0-.079.037c-.21.375-.444.864-.608 1.25a18.27 18.27 0 0 0-5.487 0 12.64 12.64 0 0 0-.617-1.25.077.077 0 0 0-.079-.037A19.736 19.736 0 0 0 3.677 4.37a.07.07 0 0 0-.032.027C.533 9.046-.32 13.58.099 18.057a.082.082 0 0 0 .031.057 19.9 19.9 0 0 0 5.993 3.03.078.078 0 0 0 .084-.028 14.09 14.09 0 0 0 1.226-1.994.076.076 0 0 0-.041-.106 13.107 13.107 0 0 1-1.872-.892.077.077 0 0 1-.008-.128 10.2 10.2 0 0 0 .372-.292.074.074 0 0 1 .077-.01c3.928 1.793 8.18 1.793 12.062 0a.074.074 0 0 1 .078.01c.12.098.246.198.373.292a.077.077 0 0 1-.006.127 12.299 12.299 0 0 1-1.873.892.077.077 0 0 0-.041.107c.36.698.772 1.362 1.225 1.993a.076.076 0 0 0 .084.028 19.839 19.839 0 0 0 6.002-3.03.077.077 0 0 0 .032-.054c.5-5.177-.838-9.674-3.549-13.66a.061.061 0 0 0-.031-.03zM8.02 15.33c-1.183 0-2.157-1.085-2.157-2.419 0-1.333.956-2.419 2.157-2.419 1.21 0 2.176 1.096 2.157 2.42 0 1.333-.956 2.418-2.157 2.418zm7.975 0c-1.183 0-2.157-1.085-2.157-2.419 0-1.333.955-2.419 2.157-2.419 1.21 0 2.176 1.096 2.157 2.42 0 1.333-.946 2.418-2.157 2.418z"/>
      </svg>
      Connexion avec Discord
    </a>
    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Email</h3>
        <p>Récupération de votre email Discord</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Serveurs</h3>
        <p>Rejoignez des serveurs automatiquement</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Tableau de bord</h3>
        <p>Gérez vos connexions</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
